          <h2 class="text-[28px] font-bold text-[#202318] lg:text-[34px]" style="font-family:var(--font-display)">
            Start Investing in Equities Today
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 max-w-lg text-[14px] text-[#202318]/70">
            Open a free Demat account in under 10 minutes — ₹0 delivery brokerage, SEBI-registered research calls, and a dedicated relationship manager.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex shrink-0 flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/about/open-demat-account/" class="inline-flex h-12 w-[220px] items-center justify-center rounded-[6px] bg-[#202318] text-[14px] font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:bg-black">Open Demat Account</a>
          <a href="/about/support/" class="inline-flex h-12 w-[220px] items-center justify-center rounded-[6px] border border-[#202318]/30 text-[14px] font-medium text-[#202318] transition-all hover:bg-[#202318]/10">Talk to an RM</a>
